	DURGA PUJA      October 14 at Ramakrishna Math, Baranagar: Sri Sri Chandipaath at 7 am; Recitation of hymn on Mahisasuramardini and devotional songs of Ma Durga by devotees at 6.10 pm.     October 14 at Bidhannagar Ramakrishna Vivekananda Kendra, DD-44 Salt Lake: Maha Saptami Puja. Naba Patrika Snan amp; Pravesh Sthapan, Saptamyadi Kalparambh amp; Saptami Bihit Puja Prashasta by 9.28 am.     October 14 - 16 at Ramakrishna Math, Belur Math, Howrah: Sri Sri Durga Puja will be celebrated at Belur Math. Special launch services throughout the day by West Bengal Surface Transport Corporation Limited. Today: Saptami puja begins at 5.40 am; Pushpanjali after Bhogarati of Sri Sri Devi; Evening aarati of Sri Sri Devi after aarati of Sri Sri Thakur.     Till October 17: Cycle Pure Agarbathies presents Rhythm Dhaker Ladai 2010, a contest for the dhakis now in its seventh year takes place across 45 Puja pandals in the city and surrounding areas. Judges: Pandit Ajoy Chakrabarty, Koushiki Chakrabarty, Chandrabali Rudra Dutta and Mamata Shankar.     
